========================================================================================

TowerWitch - GPS-enabled Amateur Radio Tower & Repeater Locator

This software is designed for amateur radio operators, emergency services, and 
communications enthusiasts to locate nearby radio infrastructure using GPS positioning.

Key Features:
- Real-time GPS integration
- Amateur radio repeater databases
- Emergency communication services (ARMER, Skywarn)
- Touch-optimized interface for mobile operation
- Night mode for field operations

For more information, documentation, and support:
https://github.com/yourusername/TowerWitch

Amateur Radio Emergency Communication:
This software supports emergency preparedness and public service communications.
Emergency services integration includes weather spotting networks and public
safety radio systems where legally accessible.

73s and stay safe!

